```console
$ app geoip --help
`GeoIP` tooling (list/lookup/export)

Usage: app geoip [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list    List country codes available in the database
  lookup  Lookup if an IP is contained in the `GeoIP` database
  export  Export a country as rule-set JSON
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -c, --config <CONFIG>
          Set configuration file path(s)
  -f, --file <FILE>
          `GeoIP` database file (text or MMDB) [default: geoip.db]
  -C, --config-directory <CONFIG_DIRECTORY>
          Set configuration directory path(s) (non-recursive, *.json)
  -D, --directory <DIRECTORY>
          Set working directory
      --disable-color
          Disable color output
  -h, --help
          Print help

$ app geosite --help
