$ app ruleset --help
Rule-set management (validate/compile/etc.)

Usage: app ruleset [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  validate   Validate a rule-set file (JSON or binary)
  info       Show information about a rule-set file
  format     Format a JSON rule-set (prettify)
  decompile  Decompile a binary .srs file into JSON source format
  match      Match helper: test whether a domain/IP/port matches the rule-set
  compile    Compile a JSON rule-set into binary .srs
  convert    Convert between JSON and SRS formats based on extension
  merge      Merge multiple rule-set files (append rules) and write to output
  upgrade    Upgrade rule-set version (JSON or SRS input)
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

